## Examples 4 & 5 (Choice)

```elixir
res = prove ~f"""
(![X:$i]: ?[Y:$i]: r @ X @ Y) => (?[F:$i>$i]: ![X:$i]: r @ X @ (F @ X))
"""

format_result res
# THM
```

```elixir
render res
```

```elixir
res = prove ~f"""
?[E:($i>$o)>$i]: ![P:$i>$o]: ( (![Y:$i]: P @ Y) => P @ (E @ P) )
"""

format_result res
# THM
```

```elixir
render res
```

